               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t16900605-4-defend37" type="defendantName">
                     Solomon 
                     Hewet
                  <interp inst="t16900605-4-defend37" type="surname" value="Hewet"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-defend37" type="given" value="Solomon"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-defend37" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was Indicted of <rs id="t16900605-4-off17" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-off17" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-off17" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               Felony and Burglary, for stealing from 
                     
                        <persName id="t16900605-4-victim39" type="victimName">
                           Nicholas 
                           Bernard
                        <interp inst="t16900605-4-victim39" type="surname" value="Bernard"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16900605-4-victim39" type="given" value="Nicholas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16900605-4-victim39" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16900605-4-off17 t16900605-4-victim39"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                   on the <rs id="t16900605-4-cd18" type="crimeDate">15th day of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16900605-4-off17 t16900605-4-cd18"></join> last, 8 pair of Mens Shoes value 20 s. 10 pair of Womens Shoes 20 s. 10 pair more of Mens Shoes 40 s. a Padlock 6 d.
            </rs> The Evidence deposed, that the Prisoner was found in the Prosecutor's shop about 11 of the clock at night, and some of the Shoes were found in his custody. The Prisoner denied the Fact, yet he was found <rs id="t16900605-4-verdict19" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-verdict19" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs> of the Felony. Taking hold of Their Majesties <rs id="t16900605-4-punish20" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-punish20" type="punishmentCategory" value="noPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16900605-4-punish20" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="pardon"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t16900605-4-defend37 t16900605-4-punish20"></join>
               Pardon
            </rs>, the Prisoner was discharged.</p>
